						               													<description>From the mind of internet funny-guy Jerma985 comes the Grotto Beasts! Trading Card Game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players build a deck of cards they will use to battle against an opponent to become a champion. Cards come in four types: Beast, Wish, Grotto and Challenger. Beast cards use their power to attack an opponent's team, while the Grotto cards boost the power or abilities of Beasts. The Wish cards give players extra tricks up their sleeves to pull off special effects. Challengers are used for the special Jerma Rumble variant of the game, letting players team up with the characters of Jerma985's jermaverse.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As players summon cards from their hand, they add cards to their Summoning Pool while their opponent draws cards from their Summoning Pool. The more cards a player draws, the stronger the cards a player may summon.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
